name: Fuzzy The Friendly Fox
description:
He was the first of the 4 we ordered. His name is Fuzzy. I'm aware he is a cheapo animatronic but for the price we bought him for, you would think he would come with a functioning voice box, it almost feels like we got scammed, at
least that's what the company thinks, I think the company is just cheap and lazy. 

4/12/95 - 30 days till opening
